;TELETYPE INPUT CHANNEL 7 ROUTINE
;RUN EVERY SO OFTEN TO MOVE CHARACTERS FROM BIG BUFFER TO LINE BUFFERS,
;GENERATE ECHOS AND HANDLE CARRIER TRANSITIONS
